{"tid":765654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歡樂天地九展復活 8月8日搶先夾公仔","createTime":"2018-08-03T03:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T01:17:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"13550ec9f0f54bf7da4c52dc00f8f0195cd85a43","tid":765654,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180803/_2018080309584387296.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180803%2F_2018080309584387296.jpg&h=6a828ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n充滿童年回憶的歡樂天地，下周三（8日）於九龍灣國際展貿中心復活啦！<br />\n<br />\n歡樂天地將重新開業，位於九展分店門外部分夾公仔機本月8日率先試業。觀樂天地facebook貼出多張圖片，相中所見，雖然正在裝修，但夾公仔機和禮品已準備就緒，多啦A夢和唐老鴨都滿心期待地跟新主人回家。<br />\n<br />\n無論是七十後或八十後，歡樂天地絕對是歡樂的代名詞。創立於1982年的歡樂天地，1987年前名為「出奇老鼠」，曾是香港上市公司。1990年代初，歡樂天地收歸「八佰伴」集團旗下。<br />\n<br />\n全盛時期，歡樂天地設有25間遍布全港的分店，包括太古城中心、沙田新城市廣場、屯門市廣場等。不過，日本「八佰伴」1997年破產，歡樂天地放盤，最終售予中資機構。其後因經濟低迷，加上競爭對手「美國冒險樂園」的出現，歡樂天地生意迅速萎縮，終於1999年關門大吉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180803/_2018080309591763164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180803%2F_2018080309591763164.jpg&h=b82080ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180803/_2018080310052771427.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180803%2F_2018080310052771427.jpg&h=838a8bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180803/_2018080310062121165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180803%2F_2018080310062121165.jpg&h=5351d47e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/781858-香港-【